# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000037> (secondary creep region)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000037> "https://www.iso.org/standard/67737.html")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000037> "secondary creep region"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000037> "The stage of creep where the creep rate becomes nearly constant and steady-state deformation dominates.")
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000037> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000009>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/CTO_1000038> (tertiary creep region)

